## Remarks  

> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="dabbe-716">O <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader> classe está obsoleta no [!INCLUDE[dnprdnext](~/includes/dnprdnext-md.md)].</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dabbe-716">The <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader> class is obsolete in [!INCLUDE[dnprdnext](~/includes/dnprdnext-md.md)].</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dabbe-717">Você pode criar uma validação <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> instância usando o <xref:System.Xml.XmlReaderSettings> classe e o <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.Create%2A> método.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dabbe-717">You can create a validating <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> instance by using the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReaderSettings> class and the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.Create%2A> method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dabbe-718">Para obter mais informações, consulte a seção de Comentários da página de referência <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dabbe-718">For more information, see the Remarks section of the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> reference page.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="dabbe-719">O usuário precisa para testar o tipo retornado.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dabbe-719">The user needs to test for the returned type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dabbe-720">Por exemplo,</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dabbe-720">For example,</span></span>  

```csharp  
object obj = vreader.SchemaType;  
 if (obj is XmlSchemaType)  
 {  
   XmlSchemaType st = (XmlSchemaType)obj;  
   // use XmlSchemaType object  
 }  
 if (obj is XmlSchemaDatatype)  
 {  
   XmlSchemaDatatype sd = (XmlSchemaDatatype)obj;  
   Type vt = sd.ValueType;  
   // use XmlSchemaDatatype object  
       }  
```  

 <span data-ttu-id="dabbe-721">Se a validação de esquema XML está sendo executada, o `XmlSchemaType` ou `XmlSchemaDatatype` corresponde ao elemento atual que está sendo lido.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dabbe-721">If XML Schema validation is being performed, the `XmlSchemaType` or `XmlSchemaDatatype` corresponds to the current element being read.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dabbe-722">Se a definição de tipo de documento (validação de DTD) estiver sendo executada, essa propriedade retornará `null`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dabbe-722">If document type definition (DTD validation) is being performed, this property returns `null`.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="dabbe-723">`XmlSchemaDatatype` será retornado se o elemento atual ou atributo, é um tipo simples que pode especificar restrições de validação especiais nos tipos simples, como min e max.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dabbe-723">`XmlSchemaDatatype` is returned if the current element, or attribute, is a simple type that can specify special validation constraints on the simple types, like min and max.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="dabbe-724">`XmlSchemaSimpleType` será retornado se o elemento atual ou atributo, é um simpleType definida pelo usuário.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dabbe-724">`XmlSchemaSimpleType` is returned if the current element, or attribute, is a user defined simpleType.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="dabbe-725">`XmlSchemaComplexType` será retornado se o elemento atual é um complexType definida pelo usuário.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dabbe-725">`XmlSchemaComplexType` is returned if the current element is a user defined complexType.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dabbe-726">Esse tipo não pode ser retornado por atributos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dabbe-726">This type cannot be returned by attributes.</span></span>  

> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="dabbe-727">Se <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.ValidationType%2A> tiver sido definido para ValidationType.None, nenhuma informação de tipo de dados é fornecida de esquemas ou DTDs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dabbe-727">If <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.ValidationType%2A> has been set to ValidationType.None, no data type information is provided from either schemas or DTDs.</span></span>  

> [!CAUTION]
>  <span data-ttu-id="dabbe-728">Depois de chamar <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.Close%2A>, SchemaType retornará Null.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dabbe-728">After calling <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.Close%2A>, SchemaType will return Null.</span></span>  



